 3 Juli 1916 Monday Usual duti occupi day . Prepar for a day 's sport dinner at night ? for tomorrow prematur knock on the head by order come thro ? that Amb . must remov to --- by 2 p.m on morrow . Active prepar for trek . Toni come across after tea . Tell of his adventur out at the trench yesterday . He hold the distinct of go into trench first of the Trio . Walk part of way back with him had part cup at crossroad . When shall we meet again ! soon I hope . I miss the good old chap also Bob more than I can tell . Dinner smoke concert in messroom at 9 p.m. Beer skit . Some enjoy .
